¬∑ Wire ampacity tables
¬∑ Conduit fill charts
¬∑ Color code references
¬∑ Motor FLA tables

Field Reference (Mobile)

¬∑ Essential formulas
¬∑ Quick conversions
¬∑ Offline access
¬∑ Favorites system

Features for Professional Use

For Electricians:

¬∑ Quick code lookups on job site
¬∑ Accurate calculations for installations
¬∑ Violation checking for inspections
¬∑ Mobile access without internet

For Inspectors:

¬∑ Reference during inspections
¬∑ Violation documentation
¬∑ Code verification

For Students:

¬∑ Learning NEC requirements
¬∑ Practice calculations
¬∑ Study reference materials

Development

To add more code sections or calculators:

1. Update referenceDatabase.js with new data
